      <description><![CDATA[<div class="element-set">
    <h2>Dublin Core</h2>
        <div id="dublin-core-title" class="element">
        <h3>Title</h3>
                                    <div class="element-text">&quot;Review of the Age-of-Consent Legislation in Texas&quot;[Magazine Article, 1895]</div>
